{"tid":864444,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［人間慘劇］真．大炎火炙菊","createTime":"2018-10-16T08:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T11:34:03.000Z","uid":123825,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd5806093e4cbdeaff13595ddb377c90fe2e462","tid":864444,"uid":123825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:06:15.000Z","msg":"有咩慘撚得過食完辣野肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚食完辛辣麵<br />\n講真 都真係唔係話好辣<br />\n今朝開始肚痾<br />\n初初都無乜是 <br />\n攪下腸沙咪當清下條垃圾腸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n痾到第二次開始<br />\n粒嫩菊有陣陣暖意<br />\n再又暖意變成火燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n粒菊每收縮一下<br />\n都好似被無窮盡嘅熱水攻襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每次再去廁所<br />\n都要鼓足勇氣<br />\n去受地獄無間火焰嘅煎熬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我又坐係屎塔上<br />\n第六次鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不願活鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807410066ff3bde495d84c4041d6ad845732d616","tid":864444,"uid":95470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"5.5/10"},{"pid":"e155bc73eacce7b5ce6413f1aebad2df1b4c0170","tid":864444,"uid":123825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"807410066ff3bde495d84c4041d6ad845732d616","tid":864444,"uid":95470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"5.5/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:55:38.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我粒菊仲燒緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beacf24debf4c6f5dd6912585a1d68ed6202f644","tid":864444,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"過咗火啦 3分比多你"},{"pid":"0ec5f2c67ec06b291b3f83eeb8e5d